metadata.title: Kate and Laurel Lintz Modern Industrial Wood and Metal Floating Wall Shelves with Black Metal Frame, Rustic White
features: A modern decorative, design, these floating wood wall shelves are secured with a smart black metal frame that is 30.5 inches tall and holds 3 wood shelf boards

Use these rustic floating shelves for organizing and displaying your favorite home accents. They would look fabulous in a bathroom, kitchen, dining room or in any room of the house that has usable wall space
Each shelf is 26-inches wide by 7-inches deep leaving plenty of room to display your favorite framed photos, ornaments and books
Keyhole hangers are attached to the frame for easy secure wall display
Shelves are easy to assemble with all hardware included; Shelves are constructed of wood with a metal frame
description: Rustic coastal design combined with smart functionality makes up this floating wall shelf. Constructed with a black metal frame supporting three wood shelves, this floating shelving can be used to display your books, photo frames, or knickknacks in your living room or home office. Each shelf measures 26 inches wide by 7 inches deep and there are 12 inches of vertical space between each shelf. The display dimensions of the floating shelves are 26 inches wide by 7.25 inches deep by 30.5 inches high. This decorative wall shelving is versatile, functional, and will be a beautiful accent in any room of the home.
